channel.title: Portforwarding Weird problem?
channel.description: Alright so I portforwarded a long time ago and now it just stopped working. I think it maybe 'cause we got the Vonage phone service.. not sure. My modem connects to the Vonage box thing then the Vonage thing connects to my router. So I think it's the reason my portforwarding isn't working. I've read all tut's on portforwarding and none of them worked. I even tried that 317 auto-portforwarder, and that didn't work either. Can someone help me, please? :( [center]Thank You.[/center]
